// ── DESTINATION: vercel.json (repo root, next to the hybrid Cargo.toml) ───────
// GOVERNING DOC: knowledge/04-vercel-rust-runtime.md §4
// Configures ONLY the web build + output dir. There is NO "functions" block:
// the official @vercel/rust runtime detects the function from the root
// Cargo.toml [[bin]]. `--package {{crate_prefix}}-web` is mandatory (dx can't
// infer the crate in a multi-binary workspace). The copy uses no `|| true` so it
// fails loudly rather than shipping a blank site.
//
// NOTE: strip these `//` comments before use — vercel.json is strict JSON.
// ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
{
  "$schema": "https://openapi.vercel.sh/vercel.json",
  "buildCommand": "mkdir -p public && dx bundle --platform web --package {{crate_prefix}}-web --release && cp -r target/dx/{{crate_prefix}}-web/release/web/public/* public/",
  "outputDirectory": "public"
}
